OL,3,CExplained: Why are Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport's night flights so
OL,5,Ccontroversial?
OL,7,FBirmingham Airport will now have more
OL,8,Fnight flights - despite locals
OL,9,Fclaiming it is bad for their health.
OL,11,FSolihull Council has agreed to
OL,12,Fincrease the cap on the number of
OL,13,Fnight flights that can leave the
OL,14,Fairport between 11:30pm and 6am.
OL,16,FPreviously, only 5% of the airport's
OL,17,Fflights were allowed to be at night.
OL,18,FThe new figure is 7.2%, a 40% increase.
OL,20,FWhy has it been changed?
