OL,3,CExplained: Why are Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport's night flights so
OL,5,Ccontroversial?
OL,7,FBirmingham Airport and Solihull
OL,8,FCouncil want to increase the airports
OL,9,Fcapacity because more people are
OL,10,Fflying. It's predicted there will be
OL,11,Fabout 94,000 flights in an out of
OL,12,FBirmingham this year.
OL,14,FWhile the 5% cap hasn't gone up since
OL,15,F2009, passenger numbers have. There
OL,16,Fare expected to be 13 million people
OL,17,Ftravelling through Birmingham airport
OL,18,Fthis year, 40% more than 16 years ago.
