OL,3,CExplained: Why are Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport's night flights so
OL,5,Ccontroversial?
OL,7,FThe airport has said increasing the 5%
OL,8,Fcap could see an extra #225 million
OL,9,Fcontributed to the economy and lead to
OL,10,Fmore than 3,500 jobs being created.
OL,12,FWhy are local residents up in arms?
OL,14,FThere are a range of reasons, some
OL,15,Ffocus on the environmental
OL,16,Fconsequences of having more flights
OL,17,Fand others believe it will be bad for
OL,18,Ftheir health.
