OL,3,CExplained: Why are Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport's night flights so
OL,5,Ccontroversial?
OL,7,FShe told ITV News Central: "The WHO is
OL,8,Fextremely clear that at a limit of
OL,9,Fover 40 decibels you start to get
OL,10,Fhealth effects of sleep disturbance.
OL,12,F"The consequences of this can be
OL,13,Fobesity, attention deficit type
OL,14,Fdisorders and for older people it can
OL,15,Fincrease the risk of heart disorders."
OL,17,FShe adds that the area around
OL,18,FBirmingham Airport is also one of the
OL,19,Fmost densely populated of any urban
OL,20,Fairport.
