OL,3,CExplained: Why are Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport's night flights so
OL,5,Ccontroversial?
OL,7,FRosamond Nicholson said: "There are
OL,8,Fmore people living within the 50
OL,9,Fdecibel noise contour of Birmingham
OL,10,Fairports than Stansted and Gatwick's
OL,11,F55 decibel corridor combined."
OL,13,FThis view is supported by a study
OL,14,Freleased on Wednesday which found
OL,15,Fpeople who live near airports may be
OL,16,Fat greater risk of poor heart health.
OL,18,FThe team, from University College
OL,19,FLondon, found people living in higher
OL,20,Fnoise areas had worse heart health
OL,21,Fthan those in quieter areas.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
