OL,3,CExplained: Why are Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport's night flights so
OL,5,Ccontroversial?
OL,7,FThose near airports had stiffer and
OL,8,Fthicker heart muscles that contracted
OL,9,Fand expanded less easily and were less
OL,10,Fefficient at pumping blood around the
OL,11,Fbody.
OL,13,FThe team said this can lead to heart
OL,14,Fattacks, life-threatening abnormal
OL,15,Fheart rhythms, and strokes.
OL,17,FThe scientists monitored 3,635 people
OL,18,Fwho lived by airports in Birmingham,
OL,19,FLondon and Manchester.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
