OL,3,CExplained: Why are Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport's night flights so
OL,5,Ccontroversial?
OL,7,FSenior author Dr Gaby Captur, of the
OL,8,FUCL Institute of Cardiovascular
OL,9,FScience said: "Our study is
OL,10,Fobservational so we cannot say with
OL,11,Fcertainty that high levels of aircraft
OL,12,Fnoise caused these differences in
OL,13,Fheart structure and function.
OL,15,F"However, our findings add to a
OL,16,Fgrowing body of evidence that aircraft
OL,17,Fnoise can adversely affect heart
OL,18,Fhealth and our health more generally."
