OL,3,CExplained: Why are Birmingham
OL,4,CAirport's night flights so
OL,5,Ccontroversial?
OL,7,FBirmingham Airport said that
OL,8,Findependent noise surveys were carried
OL,9,Fout as part of the consultation
OL,10,Fprocess, and they found that the
OL,11,Faverage night noise wouldn't increase.
OL,13,FSolihull Council's planning committee
OL,14,Fsaid, despite the many objections from
OL,15,Fneighbouring residents, "no adverse
OL,16,Fimpacts have been identified which
OL,17,Fwould significantly and demonstrably
OL,18,Foutweigh the significant benefits."
